  "description": "Density at ceiling — 0.98. Grain size tiny at 0.04. posScatter 1.0. pitchScatter 0.6. This is the full granular fog: hundreds of simultaneous micro-grains arriving from random positions at random pitches. The played note survives as a center-of-mass tendency, a gravitational midpoint in the harmonic chaos. Filter open and resonant. This is how a synthesizer becomes weather.",
